name: Hitchcock Collection – Limited Edition Print – The Birds
description: A series of 90 hand numbered, hand signed limited edition prints celebrating Alfred Hitchcock's cinematic masterpiece 'The Birds'. 2012 marks the 90th anniversary of what is believed to be Alfred Hitchcock’s first directorial effort: an unfinished, now lost silent film called No. 13. To commemorate this event 90 editions of minimalist images from The Hitchcock Collection are available to buy. The supporting text on the poster highlights the film title and year of release, as well as the hand numbered limited edition. More details at www.ryantym.com Dimensions A3 (210mm x 297mm) Unframed Materials Printed on Fedrigoni Constellation Snow Ultrabright White, Uncoated Paper, 280gsm
